The first screenshot showing the Royal Mail integration is a direct integration with Royal Mail and does not require EasyPost to connect your Royal Mail OBA account.
&nbsp;
However, this integration is currently on hold and is not supported at the moment. Additionally, there is an important requirement from Royal Mail: merchants must process at least 25,000 shipments per year to qualify for API access. If your OBA account meets this requirement, please let us know.
&nbsp;
Regarding the second option, i.e., the Royal Mail Rates option, connecting this app allows you to display Royal Mail services and rates to customers using the Royal Mail rate card. This enables customers to select Royal Mail services and place orders.
&nbsp;
However, with this option, you will not be able to generate shipping labels through the plugin. Once you receive orders with Royal Mail services, you would need to generate and print Royal Mail labels outside the plugin.
&nbsp;
By connecting your Royal Mail account through EasyPost, you will be able to display rates, generate labels, and fulfill orders directly from the plugin.
